---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-20">
    
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
        Buy More, Save More Quantity Bundles in Shopify (No App)
      </h2>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Developed a custom “Buy More, Save More” quantity bundle system in Shopify without relying on any third-party apps. This feature encourages customers to purchase higher quantities by offering tiered discounts directly on the product page.
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Customers can clearly see value-driven options like “Buy 2 → Save 10%” and “Buy 3 → Save 20% (Best Value)”, making it easier for them to choose higher bundles and increasing Average Order Value (AOV).
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        The solution was implemented using Liquid and JavaScript, ensuring it works seamlessly across Shopify themes while keeping performance fast and lightweight compared to app-based alternatives.
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        The UI is fully customizable, allowing merchants to highlight best offers, display dynamic pricing, and create a conversion-focused shopping experience without recurring app costs.
      </p>
      
      <!-- CTA Links -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a 
          href="https://ecomwonk.com/posts/add-custom-badges-on-shopify-products-without-app/" 
          target="_blank"
          class="text-blue-400 font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">
          Read Full Blog
        </a>

        <a 
          href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2w2GkDnU7kQ" 
          target="_blank"
          class="text-blue-400 font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">
          Watch Full Video
        </a>
      </div>
    
      <div class="aspect-video w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full rounded-xl shadow-lg"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/voH0c2v80X8?autoplay=1&mute=1&loop=1&playlist=voH0c2v80X8&controls=0&modestbranding=1"
          title="Shopify Quantity Bundles Feature"
          allow="autoplay; encrypted-media"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
        Add FREE GIFT to Shopify Cart Without Any App
      </h2>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Built a custom Shopify feature that automatically adds a free gift to the cart when customers reach a specific spending threshold without using any third-party apps.
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        The solution includes a dynamic cart progress system that motivates users to unlock rewards like free shipping and free gifts. As customers add items, the progress bar updates in real time, encouraging higher spending and improving Average Order Value (AOV).
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Implemented using Liquid and JavaScript in the Shopify Dawn theme, this lightweight approach avoids app bloat, improves performance, and gives full control over customization.
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        The system intelligently handles cart updates automatically adding the gift when the threshold is met and removing it if the cart value drops ensuring a seamless user experience.
      </p>
      
      <!-- CTA Links -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a 
          href="https://ecomwonk.com/posts/add-free-gift-to-cart-shopify-without-app/" 
          target="_blank"
          class="text-blue-400 font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">
          Read Full Blog
        </a>

        <a 
          href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6YlGCUmJ6VY" 
          target="_blank"
          class=" text-blue-400 font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">
          Watch Full Video
        </a>
      </div>
    
      <div class="aspect-video w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full rounded-xl"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/a6yeeiXlzC4?autoplay=1&mute=1&loop=1&playlist=a6yeeiXlzC4&controls=0&showinfo=0&modestbranding=1"
          title="Free Gift Shopify Feature"
          allow="autoplay; encrypted-media"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Project 1 -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
        Product Engraving Personalization on product page without any 3rd party app
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Implemented a custom laser engraving personalization feature on the Shopify product page without using any third-party apps.
        Customers can enable the engraving option, enter their custom text, and the additional engraving cost is automatically applied.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        To overcome Shopify’s limitation of modifying the original product price, I developed a solution where the engraving is added as a separate linked line item in the cart.
        The engraving text is stored with the product and remains visible in the cart, checkout, and final order.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        This solution works with any Shopify theme and provides a lightweight alternative to expensive personalization apps while maintaining store performance.
      </p>

      <div class="aspect-video w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full rounded-xl"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rZQ3PgyoQPE"
          title="Project Walkthrough"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Project 2 -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
        Custom Theme Enhancements & Large-Scale Review Migration from Ebay to Shopify
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Worked on a Prestige theme store with advanced customizations beyond the default layout.
        Redesigned the header with a centered search bar and repositioned navigation for better UX.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Built custom tab sections, dynamic brand pages using metaobjects, and a dedicated brand template showcasing products and collections.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Migrated over 200,000 reviews from eBay, ensuring proper formatting and seamless integration into Shopify.
      </p>

      <div class="aspect-video w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full rounded-xl"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LrJyXgu81hk"
          title="Project Walkthrough"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Project 3 -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
        Advanced Theme Customization & SKU-Based Product Grouping Automation using Shopify Flow
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Mobile Navigation Rebuilt</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Converted navigation into tab-based layout</li>
            <li>Displayed first-level items instantly on drawer open</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Dynamic Product Grouping</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Grouped products using first 7 digits of SKU</li>
            <li>Automated grouping via Shopify Flow</li>
            <li>Auto updates on product changes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Variant-like Experience</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Dynamic URL + content updates</li>
            <li>AJAX-based product refresh</li>
            <li>Swatches on product, collection, and upsells</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Result</h3>
          <p>
            Created a scalable system where independent products behave like variants without restructuring the catalog.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aspect-video w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full rounded-xl"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mrFB1yozm_k"
          title="Project Walkthrough"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Project 4 -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">
        Infinite Scroll for Shopify Collection Pages (Filter & Sort Compatible)
      </h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Developed a custom infinite scroll solution for Shopify collection pages that works seamlessly with filtering and sorting, without using any third-party apps.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Unlike most implementations, this solution dynamically loads products based on active filters and continues working flawlessly.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        Lightweight and scalable, this approach improves UX while maintaining performance.
      </p>

      <div class="aspect-video w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full rounded-xl"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RXLZAwQLhfI"
          title="Project Walkthrough"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- YouTube -->
    <section class="text-center space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">YouTube Channel</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        Trusted by 1600+ subscribers, I share my learnings regarding Shopify development.
      </p>

      <script src="https://apis.google.com/js/platform.js"></script>

      <div
        class="g-ytsubscribe"
        data-channelid="UCylxuBh0e-M5_HE24xIzM0w"
        data-layout="full"
        data-theme="dark"
        data-count="default">
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LinkedIn -->
    <section class="text-center space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">LinkedIn Profile</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        Trusted by 4000+ people on LinkedIn, I share my learnings publicly.
      </p>

      <script src="https://platform.linkedin.com/badges/js/profile.js" async defer></script>

      <div
        class="badge-base LI-profile-badge mx-auto"
        data-locale="en_US"
        data-size="large"
        data-theme="dark"
        data-type="HORIZONTAL"
        data-vanity="saadsaif97"
        data-version="v1">
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
